FBIS4-16801 "drsov076_g_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Deputy Premier on Money Merger Ratification Deputy Premier on Money Merger Ratification WS1904133694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1000 GMT 19 Apr 94 WS1904133694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Belarusian BFN [Text] Belarusian Deputy Prime Minister Mikhail Myasnikovich believes that the Belarusian Supreme Soviet will certainly ratify the treaty with Russia on the unification of monetary systems. Speaking at a news conference at the third annual session of the Council of European Bank Managers, he said that Russian Central Bank Chairman Viktor Gerashchenko accepts the Belarusian approach toward a common emission policy within the framework of the unified monetary system.
